			<title>Widget Tests success</title>
			<section>
				<title>Binding Applications rule</title>
				<para>
					All Quality management applications of all your projects can be binded to the widget. 
					For configuring applications to bind, please refer to section <xref linkend="widgetCommonSetting" endterm="widgetCommonSettingXref" />.
				</para>
			</section>
			<section>
				<title>Overview</title>
				<para>
					This widget show the tests success evolution for one resource, grouped by test result, in the form of a stacked column chart.
					You can hide or show tests results by clicking on results name and icon in the legend.
				</para>
				<figure>
					<title>Example : Widget tests success evolution overview
					</title>
					<mediaobject>
						<imageobject>
							<imagedata align="center"
								fileref="07-Widget-TestsSuccess-Overview.png" />
						</imageobject>
					</mediaobject>
				</figure>
				
			</section>
			<section>
				<title>Widget parameters</title>
				<figure>
					<title>Configuration of widget properties</title>
					<mediaobject>
						<imageobject>
							<imagedata align="center"
								fileref="07-Widget-TestsSuccess-Setting.png" />
						</imageobject>
					</mediaobject>
				</figure>
				<para>
					This menu allow you to :
					<itemizedlist>
						<listitem>
							<para>Modify widget title in your dashboard, by editing the "name" field
							</para>
						</listitem>
						<listitem>
							<para>Select the resource and the number of builds you want to use in the widget
							</para>
						</listitem>
						<listitem>
							<para>Save your modifications</para>
						</listitem>
						<listitem>
							<para>Return to dashboard, by clicking on the return button at top right.
							</para>
						</listitem>
					</itemizedlist>
				</para>
			</section>
</section>
